(24, 'Email Marketing Services in Sonipat - SMS Services', '<p>Boost your business with <strong>email marketing services in India</strong>. See how Apricorn Solutions help&nbsp;a Haryana shop grow using expert email marketing strategies.</p>', '<p>Sonipat is the most popular district in Haryana and in the centre of Sonipat. Rohit Malik was a second-generation shopkeeper who operated his family\'s textile business, Malik Fabrics, in the middle of Sonipat, nearby Sector 12. The store has been remaining on word-of-mouth and walk-ins for years. However, things were change. Customers were using their phones to browse instead of exploring markets, and new boutiques were opening up. Rohit realized he needed to change things.<br>His curiosity was piqued when his Delhi cousin mentioned something one evening while enjoying a cup of chai.<br>\"Bhai, why don\'t you use email marketing? We now receive all of our online orders in this way!<br><br>Rohit had questions. He asked, \"Who reads emails anymore?\"<br>However, the idea continued to exist.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Digital Revolution</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Rohit made a decision to try it out. He collaborated&nbsp;with a regional Indian email marketing service provider (Apricorn Solutions).&nbsp;they&nbsp;aware about&nbsp;Sonipat\'s people taste&nbsp;in the term of&nbsp;digital trends.</p>\r\n<p>They started out small. A festival&nbsp;offer for Karwa Chauth that featured traditional sarees was the team\'s basic email campaign. The emails were beautifully designed, with vibrant colors, attention-grabbing subject lines, and, yes, a Hindi version of \"Happy Karwa Chauth.\"</p>\r\n<p>The magic happened within days.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Over 800 customers opened the email</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">76 visited the store that week</span><br><br></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2><strong>How Did It Work?</strong></h2>\r\n<p>This campaign felt more genuine and&nbsp;randomly mass messaging. These were:</p>\r\n<p>Tailored to suit regional preferences</p>\r\n<p>Targeted according to client preferences (sarees, Kurtis, fabrics)</p>\r\n<p>Automated&mdash;thank-you notes, birthday greetings, and festival wishes were sent automatically</p>\r\n<p>Mobile-friendly, as many of his clients read emails on their phones</p>\r\n<p>Trackable, so he could see what worked and what didn\'t</p>\r\n<p>The best part of the campaign is that a reputable email marketing service provider manage&nbsp;his campaign and deliver&nbsp;results without causing him any extra work.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>Most of the Sonipat Companies</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Rohit wasn\'t alone for long as well. A gym nearby NH44, a coaching center in Sector 14, and a cafe&nbsp;in Model Town were all now applying email marketing services in India to reach their clients in the area.</p>\r\n<p>Smart businessman adopted this and understated this is an&nbsp;effective tool to stay ahead of the developing area of&nbsp;Sonipat.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>It\'s Your Turn to Turn Your Company into the Next Big Success Story.</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Without spending thousands on advertising, email marketing services in India and for Sonipat&nbsp;can help you communicate with your customers directly, promote loyalty, and expand your business more quickly, regardless of whether you own a salon, candy store, or startup.</p>\r\n<p>Like Rohit, all you need is an email marketing service provider who knows your city and business style.</p>', 'blog_682ecc3e778e94.59666864.jpg', 'Digital Marketing Information', '2025-05-22 07:03:26', 'email-marketing-services-in-sonipat', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
